                        ðŸ“– Ler Texto Base
                    </a>
                </div>

                <div id="modalText" class="prose prose-lg text-gray-800 leading-relaxed font-serif text-justify mb-10 first-letter:text-5xl first-letter:font-bold first-letter:text-imbb-gold first-letter:mr-2 first-letter:float-left"></div>

                <div id="modalAnnualBox" class="mb-8 p-5 bg-green-50 rounded-2xl border border-green-200 hidden">
